{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":13028,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"带孝子","timestamp":1592809313,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13046,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"孝子，秀","timestamp":1592809389,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13049,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"父母的生活我们也不必干涉吧，表示自己的看法我觉得可。至少行动之前确定自己不是在撒气","timestamp":1592809409,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13133,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 确定不是在撒气。父母从dz小学开始关系就一直不好，打着为了给dz一个完整家庭的旗号苟延残喘至今。疫情期间父母争吵变本加厉，家里天然气用完了都能吵一晚上。。。","timestamp":1592809930,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13139,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 不是钓鱼，dz真的想听听大家的建议，请不要这样","timestamp":1592809991,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13160,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"差不多的感受，最后发现根本管不了的，算了吧，读完书自己出来工作自己住就完了","timestamp":1592810237,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13169,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 我觉得父母这样也不开心，关键每次还打着为我好的旗号。dz感觉这样压力很大","timestamp":1592810330,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13247,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 别听这种话。我觉得老一辈的人在一起不在一起也不是因为情感如何了，人和人的关系远比这复杂。说这些根本也没考虑你的感受，别太在意。","timestamp":1592810930,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13375,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"非常理解洞主！我家也是这样的情况，感觉从我出生起他们就已经过不下去了，一直说为了我好坚持生活了十几年，现在我妈实在受不了了就离了！可以试着向他们表达一下你不介意他们离婚的意思，但是如果父母中没有一方有下定决心分开的意思的话，感觉也很麻烦。","timestamp":1592811787,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13417,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"他们即便感情不好即便不是为了你，几十年一起的生活已经将他们的生活、社交、经济紧紧联系在一起了。他们吵得这么凶、你也离家上学了，他们却不离婚，可见他们之间的联系之紧密是现有的矛盾所分不开的。既然如此，你也不必劝分了。","timestamp":1592812040,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13440,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同。赶快拍屁股走人吧，人世间痛苦的事情多了去了，不是所有事情都管得了的。","timestamp":1592812178,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13454,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 谢谢你的建议","timestamp":1592812285,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13479,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Grace: 我确实想一走了之，但是就算是过年过节，甚至之后养老，也总得回来哇","timestamp":1592812424,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13568,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 的确啦，这也是没办法的事情。你可以选择住外面hhh，我要有钱了我就这么干。","timestamp":1592812840,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13570,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 的确啦，这也是没办法的事情。你可以选择住外面hhh，我要有钱了我就这么干。","timestamp":1592812837,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":13573,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 不知道为什么一次发了两条。","timestamp":1592812864,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":14905,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"觉得父母的关系已经发展到了虽然矛盾但依赖矛盾为生，即失去对方会因为没有矛盾而陷入虚无。没有好的解决办法","timestamp":1592821428,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":15038,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"理解洞主，我的父母现在的感情就是嫌弃和厌恶，小的时候不希望他们离婚，但长大了觉得离婚反而对他们好，不过因为妹妹的缘故离婚的事情就不好说了。我觉得洞主表达清楚你们离婚的话我很支持就好，最后结果也只能看他们自己了。","timestamp":1592822138,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":15614,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":2386,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"父母已离。本人主要的参与是协调财产分配。","timestamp":1592825597,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":2386,"reply":19,"tag":null,"text":"想让父母离婚，大家有无建议","timestamp":1592809241,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782581,"url":"","vote":{}}}